    "flock_note": "The opposite of Harmonic Gravity. Together they demonstrate the full range of the JI field system.",
    "diagnosis": "Repulsor Field proves the Harmonic Field is not just a tuning tool — it's a synthesis dimension. Repulsion creates timbres impossible through any other means."
